Quote:Just coming in here to say I see this problem all the time on TWC and glad to see we're not the only ones, but TWC does not throttle. I've seen guides like what were posted above insinuate that, but they don't.There's really no way for you to tell if they are traffic shaping or not (different from throttling). Even something as simple as letting your ISP have a preferred CDN node but it not having the capacity for the load would kill your performance without any direct malicious intent. Try a VPN and see if that fixes things.
